Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬怎麼淋成個落湯雞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路上下起了大雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  總之先把衣服脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  把熱水準備起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:48.99,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在態度上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你可可  是熱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  冬馬  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真會添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是全套的國王待遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了千秋  借套衣服給我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼態度啊  求人的方法就這麼一種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最會裝撒嬌的小女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  衣服還要等上一段時間才會乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就交給我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來糾正冬馬的小女兒脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  藤岡什麼時候來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  藤岡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  快把衣服借我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這樣下去  有點兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋衣服借來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是故意找麻煩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來夏樹昨天這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩把刷子嘛  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  看我這招  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  把那個類似手柄的東西給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬馬  再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招  看招  看招…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  男子漢的恩仇都要雙倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身為男子漢  我要從你那兒把衣服奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？只因為你是女生  沒衣服穿感到很為難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬馬   我的衣服借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  你就借衣服給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  不  借
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊  突然下起雨來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快借給我  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不借就不借
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  千秋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借衣服給我吧  我知錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好孩子  還是會求人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我房間來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好求你就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別當沒事兒人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要注意態度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香都歡迎你了  你這什麼態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了  藤岡也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脫了快脫了  總之先泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是何事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這糖真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟寶石一樣  紅豔豔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些天然色素是提取蟲子的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點兒  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個由你自己處理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吐出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分  千秋就會拿高深的知識來傷人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  說一個不傷人的高深的知識來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到蟲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  黑大蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:08:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在初春五六月雨後的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長著翅膀的雌雄黑大蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會飛出巢穴在空中進行結婚飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在聽  但還要繼續嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中舉行婚禮  這是多麼美好的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  說完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  公主的興致受到嚴重打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說一個關於千秋的高深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人不認真聽她說話就會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一個關於我的高深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑按門鈴的方式  我就能聽出門外是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…吉野來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我說是藤岡來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造謠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  快看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機雲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:10:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋難不成想用高深的知識傷害我喜歡的藤岡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機雲大多是廢氣在空中迅速冷卻凝聚而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非煙霧而是真正的雲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人工雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼盡衝著我說些討厭的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣氛算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  那不是空氣是飛機雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:41.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「空気」在日語中有氣氛和空氣兩種意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是指那個空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快看  是廢氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了是雲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:09.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次休假和春香姐姐  夏奈一起去百貨商場了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一到休假就會有作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:15.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心  還吃三色豆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一知道的就是不懂這些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是忘不了那個味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣好才覺得更加美味了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋真是喜歡藤岡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能嘗到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都已經成了千秋的指定席了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛認識藤岡的時候  他害得我夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（剛認識不久）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  那是352陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話呢  看那個畫面絕對是361
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以增加前鋒擺成343陣型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣前鋒是不是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在你換衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬和藤岡關於足球趣味相投而聊上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢的最精彩的一幕是長傳之後兩人配合拉出空位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起這個  怕是沒人料到之前會傳出那一記穿越球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本聽不懂在聊什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這意見交換得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒要記得補時哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那個…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對藤岡自我介紹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:12:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫冬馬  擔任前鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫藤岡  任何位置都能踢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何位置？  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊  真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈記一下補時時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  把你的性別告訴藤岡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬不久前剛成為千秋的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒特意去提過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好冬馬  在藤岡面前你就當男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易在足球方面能聊得那麼投機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個男子漢友好地踢球…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼了千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點兒都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之那是我的專座  讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是千秋的位置  再過去一點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  到底想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意啊  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對女生動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你挺會踢足球  但胸部囤積了過多脂肪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來鍛煉你的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行特訓吧  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…所以那是中央過人之後淩空抽射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剛才的防衛中縫又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該叫防衛中鋒  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這類話題冬馬不是很瞭解的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  冬馬今天沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冬馬之間發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了冬馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓害的啊特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就被叫醒出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的弟弟  足球少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別去特訓了  怎麼你反倒變溫順了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對了  下次千秋也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我積了脂肪再去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  春香姐姐在百貨商店…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後晨練又持續了一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終千秋還是沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋不擅長運動嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹  有事拜託別人時  這樣措辭可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面可是有模有樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一不小心就會露出馬腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的南家  非常重禮儀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那張臉孔不怎麼好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的臉不都差不多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是你眼神之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都沒有求別人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容  露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是措辭和笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很懂  但有事求春香要小心的是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭理千秋雖然很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果無視她會給春香留下壞印象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無視她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋是那個紮辮子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她扯上關係情況就複雜了  儘量避開她為妙  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,措辭和笑容…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下今日到訪有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小意思  不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  饅頭能有這個意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是蒸過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於冬馬的事有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  也只有冬馬的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為冬馬回家有些晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想請你們加以教導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才冷笑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有對冬馬說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏奈扯上關係情況就複雜了  儘量避開她為妙 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  說過沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  光知道看春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐被他盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對冬馬說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無視千秋會給春香留下壞印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無視她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對冬馬說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是置若罔聞完全不當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再嚴厲管教一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再嚴厲管教一下不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經嚴厲管教過了  結果還是行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  聽到我說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  我和她談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  今後早點兒回家怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然春香都那麼說了  就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後達成協議提早半個小時回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧  措辭果然很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是笑容比較重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是措辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求人就是為了讓我早點兒回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:12.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（第二天  傍晚）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這萵苣能再便宜一些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋多謝相助  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就這樣說不就行了  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒人一樣是指什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
